 <div class="caption">
  <p>EDS items operationalizing solastalgia [
   <a rid="B3-ijerph-16-02662" ref-type="bibr" href="#B3-ijerph-16-02662">3</a>].
  </p>
 </div>
 <table frame="hsides" rules="groups">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top:solid thin;border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Feelings of Solastalgia from Environmental Change</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Sad when looking at degraded landscapes and mine voids</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Farming lifestyle depending on good land and water is threatened by change</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Worried that valued aspects of place—clean air and water, scenery—are being lost</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Unique aspects of nature in this place are being lost</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Miss peace and quiet once enjoyed in this place</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Sad that familiar animals and plants are disappearing</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Ashamed of the way this area looks now</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Thought of my families being forced to leave this place upsets me</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Sense of belonging undermined by change</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
